OL,3,C'Things needs to change': Inside
OL,4,CEssex's mental health service crisis
OL,6,FITV News reporter Charlie Frost
OL,7,Fexplores the inquiry into the deaths
OL,8,Fof hundreds of mental health patients
OL,9,Fin Essex
OL,11,FWarning: This article contains details
OL,12,Fthat some readers may find distressing
OL,14,FCarole's youngest son Lee took his own
OL,15,Flife in 2019. Three months after
OL,16,Fleaving an Essex mental health unit.
OL,18,F"I love you so much and I'm sorry"
OL,19,Freads the letter he left for his
OL,20,Fmother.
