OL,6,F"We had to bury him the week after his
OL,7,F21st birthday. The first thought is he
OL,8,Fshould be here. He should be with us,
OL,9,Fhe should be enjoying this with us.
OL,10,FHe's missed everything and he might
OL,11,Fnot have if he'd got the help that he
OL,12,Fasked for."
OL,14,FCarole says her son, who was diagnosed
OL,15,Fwith emotionally unstable personality
OL,16,Fdisorder (EUPD), was promised therapy
OL,17,Fand a support worker in the community
OL,18,Fafter he was discharged. But, despite
OL,19,Fher calling the service weekly, it
OL,20,Fnever materialised.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/17
