OL,3,C'Things needs to change': Inside
OL,4,CEssex's mental health service crisis
OL,6,F"After Lee died, I called them and
OL,7,Fsaid to them, 'you can take him off
OL,8,Fyour books now'," she tells me.
OL,10,F"Within half an hour they were on the
OL,11,Fphone to me apologising and I've got a
OL,12,Fletter, dated that day I think or the
OL,13,Fday after, trying to sweep up the
OL,14,Fproblem."
OL,16,FI've been reporting on those so-called
OL,17,F'problems' - the failings in Essex's
OL,18,Fmental health services - since 2019.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
