OL,3,C'Things needs to change': Inside
OL,4,CEssex's mental health service crisis
OL,6,FBut families have been fighting much
OL,7,Flonger than that for change, and in
OL,8,Fthe five years I've been covering
OL,9,Ftheir progress it did feel as if there
OL,10,Fwere a few watershed moments.
OL,12,FOne was in a courtroom in Chelmsford
OL,13,Fwhen a judge handed the provider of
OL,14,Fmental health services in the county,
OL,15,FEssex Partnership University NHS
OL,16,FFoundation Trust, a #1.5 million fine
OL,17,Ffor failings that led to 11 people
OL,18,Fbeing able to take their own lives on
OL,19,Ftheir inpatient wards between 2004 and
OL,20,F2015.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
