OL,3,C'Things needs to change': Inside
OL,4,CEssex's mental health service crisis
OL,6,FCampaigners outside the crown court,
OL,7,Fled by Melanie Leahy - whose son
OL,8,FMatthew was one of those 11 - were
OL,9,Fjubilant. A small price, but progress
OL,10,Fthey felt to exposing the truth.
OL,12,FTheir big push though has been for a
OL,13,Fstatutory public inquiry into mental
OL,14,Fhealth deaths in Essex.
OL,16,FIn 2020, then-MP and Minister for
OL,17,FMental Health Nadine Dorries almost
OL,18,Fgranted their wish by ordering a non-
OL,19,Fstatutory inquiry, after Melanie
OL,20,Fraised the signatures needed for the
OL,21,Fissue to be debated in parliament.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/17
