OL,3,C'Things needs to change': Inside
OL,4,CEssex's mental health service crisis
OL,6,FAlmost four years later, the inquiry -
OL,7,Fnow in its statutory form as
OL,8,Fcampaigners wanted - will finally
OL,9,Fbegin on Monday. It will investigate
OL,10,Fhow 2,000 patients died under the care
OL,11,Fof mental health services in Essex
OL,12,Fbetween 2000 and 2023.
OL,14,FCarole is one of those taking part and
OL,15,Fshe will tell the Chair of the
OL,16,Finquiry, Baroness Lampard, of her
OL,17,Fson's story.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/17
