OL,4,CEssex's mental health service crisis
OL,6,FFormer patients will also give
OL,7,Fevidence, including one woman who told
OL,8,Fme that within three weeks of being
OL,9,Fadmitted to the Linden Centre in
OL,10,FChelmsford, she was raped by a fellow
OL,11,Fpatient. As a victim of sexual assault
OL,12,Fwe are protecting her identity.
OL,14,F"You should be saying I'm lucky that I
OL,15,Fgot the mental health support I needed
OL,16,Fat the right time but no - I'm lucky I
OL,17,Fsurvived the Linden Centre," she tells
OL,18,Fme.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/17
