OL,6,F"I can remember at least two other
OL,7,Foccasions during my time on the ward
OL,8,Fwhere other women were raped. We were
OL,9,Fcertainly not kept safe from one
OL,10,Fanother, or from ourselves.
OL,12,F"I think in my case I don't blame the
OL,13,Fpatient who raped me - he was unwell.
OL,14,FI blame the staff that weren't able to
OL,15,Fsafeguard me."
