OL,4,CEssex's mental health service crisis
OL,6,FShe says the treatment was cruel,
OL,7,Fdescribing how a staff member
OL,8,F"smirked" at her when she asked for
OL,9,Fbirth control following the rape.
OL,11,FShe also recounts how "dangerous" the
OL,12,Fward was, claiming that on occasions
OL,13,Fmembers of staff who were being paid
OL,14,Fto care for her would be distracted or
OL,15,Fsleep while on shift.
OL,17,F"I managed to abscond from the ward a
OL,18,Fcouple of times. Once I took a very
OL,19,Fserious overdose. But as I say it was
OL,20,Fa very chaotic environment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/17
