OL,3,C'Things needs to change': Inside
OL,4,CEssex's mental health service crisis
OL,6,F"It wasn't structured towards people
OL,7,Fbecoming well. It was like you were
OL,8,Fcontained in this pen and people
OL,9,Fdidn't really know what was going on."
OL,11,FThe Trust runs 35 adult inpatient
OL,12,Fwards and three for children and
OL,13,Fteenagers across the county. The acute
OL,14,Fwards are now segregated so men and
OL,15,Fwomen are separated.
OL,17,FBut, in the four years since this
OL,18,Finquiry was first ordered, concerns
OL,19,Fabout the Trust have continued to be
OL,20,Fraised.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/17
