OL,3,C'Things needs to change': Inside
OL,4,CEssex's mental health service crisis
OL,6,FIn that time coroners have written to
OL,7,Fthe Chief Executive 14 times following
OL,8,F14 separate deaths, demanding "urgent
OL,9,Faction" is taken to prevent future
OL,10,Fdeaths.
OL,12,FOne mother, whose daughter is
OL,13,Fcurrently being treated at The Lakes
OL,14,Fin Colchester, sent me photographs
OL,15,Fthat appear to show staff asleep when
OL,16,Fthey are supposed to be on suicide
OL,17,Fwatch, watching her daughter 24 hours
OL,18,Fa day.
OL,20,FShe says it's led to her daughter
OL,21,Fbeing able hurt herself on the ward.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/17
