OL,6,FIn a statement the Trust's Chief
OL,7,FExecutive Paul Scott urged anyone with
OL,8,Fconcerns around their care to contact
OL,9,Fthem.
OL,11,FMr Scott said: "We know how painful
OL,12,Fthis time will be for those who have
OL,13,Flost loved ones and our thoughts are
OL,14,Fwith them. We will continue to do all
OL,15,Fwe can to support Baroness Lampard and
OL,16,Fher team to provide the answers that
OL,17,Fpatients, families and carers are
OL,18,Fseeking.
