OL,6,F"We would urge anyone with concerns
OL,7,Faround their care, or that of a loved
OL,8,Fone, to contact us directly so that we
OL,9,Fcan offer direct support."
OL,11,FEssex Partnership University NHS
OL,12,FFoundation Trust has urged anyone
OL,13,Faffected to contact their Patient
OL,14,FAdvice and Liaison Service (PALS) on
OL,15,F0800 0857935 or epunft.pals@nhs.net
OL,17,FThe Department of Health told me the
OL,18,FSecretary of State for Health and
OL,19,FSocial Care, Wes Streeting, will soon
OL,20,Fmeet the families involved.
