OL,6,FMr Streeting said: "My thoughts are
OL,7,Fwith all those affected, including the
OL,8,Ffamilies and loved ones of those who
OL,9,Ftragically died. This is incredibly
OL,10,Fsad, with loss and suffering on a
OL,11,Flarge scale.
OL,13,F"As part of this, I will be meeting
OL,14,Fthe families shortly to hear directly
OL,15,Fof their experiences and to reassure
OL,16,Fthem that we take this issue extremely
OL,17,Fseriously.
