OL,6,F"We remain committed to assisting the
OL,7,FInquiry and will work with partners to
OL,8,Ftransform mental health care as we fix
OL,9,Four broken NHS."
OL,11,FPriya Singh, a Partner at law firm
OL,12,FHodge Jones & Allen, is working with
OL,13,F52 families who are taking part in the
OL,14,Finquiry.
OL,16,FShe told me: "People are continuing to
OL,17,Fdie because of failings at the trust.
OL,18,FThe failings are continuing to happen.
OL,19,FIt's happening potentially today,
OL,20,Fyesterday, tomorrow. This is not
OL,21,Fsomething of the past."
