OL,3,C'Things needs to change': Inside
OL,4,CEssex's mental health service crisis
OL,6,FFor grieving families like Lee's, the
OL,7,Fdamage is already done but the fight
OL,8,Fcontinues for justice and reform.
OL,10,F"I don't want any other family to go
OL,11,Fthrough what we've been through,"
OL,12,FCarole says.
OL,14,F"If one of my grandchildren need help
OL,15,Fwhen they're older hopefully if they
OL,16,Fask for help they'll get it. Things
OL,17,Fneed to change."
OL,19,FAnd that's what it's hoped this
OL,20,Finquiry will bring - truth and change.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/17
